=version 1
=resource Transactions
=method get
=endpoint /users/:id/transactions
=description Retrieves transactions for a single user.

include ../../_mixins.jade

p Hitting this endpoint displays a user's transactions, regardless of status. Transactions will be displayed in descending order by date.

h3 Parameters

table.endpoint-param-table
    tr
        td.name :id
        td.description Numeric user ID to look up transactions for.
    tr
        td.name page #[span optional]
        td.description
            | Page of results to get.
            .default 0
    tr
        td.name limit #[span optional]
        td.description
            | Number of results per page to retrieve.
            .default 50

